   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "38923d16-dc6e-42e6-84d4-b3649b9917af",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "We implemented MCMC tool in Xspec for spectral fitting and error estimation."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "id": "20e2c57b-78c4-4551-955d-5f5f0173c623",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "   All chains are now removed.\n",
      "  New chain chain.fits is now loaded.\n",
      "\n",
      "Chain chain.fits now has length 10000\n",
      "   All loaded chains have the same length.\n",
      "\n"
     ]
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 1000.8x1000.8 with 36 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "from ixpetools.utils.plot_chain import plot_corner\n",
    "specs.mcmc('chain.fits',\n",
    "          length=5000, burn=1000, nwalker=4)\n",
    "plot_corner('chain.fits')\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
